        "# Temporal Genomics Workshop: Trimming and Mapping\n",
        "\n",
        "In this workshop, we will:\n",
        "- Perform quality control using FastQC\n",
        "- Trim adapters using AdapterRemoval\n",
        "- Map reads to a reference genome using BWA\n",
        "- Process alignment files using Samtools\n"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "QP5FHb5VfYFl"
      }
    },
    {
